          <lastSummaryUpdateDate>2020-10-19T18:32:21Z</lastSummaryUpdateDate>
          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Restore Integrity of Special Prosecutors Act</b></p> <p>This bill bars an individual who has worked for a special counsel investigation or prosecution targeting a President or presidential candidate from serving in a position that requires the advice and consent of the Senate. This prohibition shall last for seven years from the end of the individual's work with the special counsel.</p>]]></text>
          <updateDate>2020-06-24T04:00:00Z</updateDate>
          <name>Introduced in Senate</name>
        </item>
